## Performance overview

The 95th percentile response time of the system being tested was **14  ms**
and **322 816 requests** were made at an average request rate of
**1 153 reqs/s**.

There were a total 322 816 failed requests, meaning 
that 100% of requests failed. The average failure rate was 
**1 191 reqs/s**, peaking at 2 383 reqs/s.

# Checks

The test had **1** different checks that were evaluated a total of
**322 816** times, of which **322 816** failed. Overall the
success rate was **0%**.

# Thresholds


The run met all of its performance expectations, with none of the defined thresholds having been
exceeded.

## Response time

The maximum response time occurred at **45 VUs**, with a response 
time of **177  ms**. The average response time at the same point in time was **13  ms**, 
with 95% of requests taking less than **15  ms**.
